MARITIME SAFETY INFORMATION WEBSITE.
1. DNC VDU UPDATED LIBRARIES ARE AVAILABLE ON NIPRNET,
   WWW AND SIPRNET WEBSITES. VDU PATCHES FOR DNC
   ARE AVAILABLE ON THE WWW EXCEPT FOR ALL LIBRARIES
   WITHIN DNC 08 AND DNC 28 AND LIBRARIES H2227825 AND H2228823.
   DNC VDU PATCHES ON THE NIPRNET CONTINUE TO BE RELOADED
   AND WILL BE AVAILABLE AS SOON AS POSSIBLE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2445/14.
